<h2 class="wikiHeadline2" id="H-Endpoints"><a href="/2013/09/11/modules-endpoints-sqlgcs-new-channel-impl-aka-new-cape-dwarf-100-beta-6#H-Endpoints">Endpoints</a></h2>

